==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fontal
<hw>Font"al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to a font,
fountain, source, or origin; original; primitive.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q> From the <qex>fontal</qex> light of ideas only can a man draw
intellectual power.</q> <rj><qau>Coleridge.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fontanel</ent>⟦br⟧
